# ðŸ“° MERN Blog Application

A full-stack **MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js)** blog application that allows users to create, edit, delete, and view blog posts with categories, authentication, and image uploads.

---

## ðŸš€ Project Overview

This project demonstrates seamless integration between the **front-end** (React + Vite) and **back-end** (Express + MongoDB), with user authentication, RESTful APIs, and image management.

### âœ¨ Key Features
- Full **CRUD** operations for blog posts  
- **User Authentication** (Register/Login using JWT)  
- **Categories** management  
- **Image uploads** via Cloudinary or local storage  
- **Comments** on posts  
- Responsive UI built with **React + Tailwind CSS**  
- Pagination, search, and filtering  
- API error handling and validation  

